              <option name="originalContent" value="&lt;!doctype html&gt;&#10;&lt;html lang=&quot;it&quot;&gt;&#10;&lt;head&gt;&#10;    &lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;/&gt;&#10;    &lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot;/&gt;&#10;    &lt;meta name=&quot;description&quot; content=&quot;Curriculum creativo di uno studente del liceo scientifico di Bitetto (BA).&quot;/&gt;&#10;    &lt;title&gt;Curriculum | Riccardo Priore&lt;/title&gt;&#10;    &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;styles/index.css&quot;/&gt;&#10;&lt;/head&gt;&#10;&lt;body&gt;&#10;&lt;header class=&quot;topbar&quot; aria-label=&quot;Navigazione principale&quot;&gt;&#10;    &lt;div class=&quot;container topbar-inner&quot;&gt;&#10;        &lt;div class=&quot;brand&quot;&gt;&#10;            &lt;span class=&quot;dot&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#10;            &lt;span&gt;Riccardo Priore - Curriculum&lt;/span&gt;&#10;        &lt;/div&gt;&#10;        &lt;nav class=&quot;nav&quot; aria-label=&quot;Sezioni curriculum&quot;&gt;&#10;            &lt;a href=&quot;#profilo&quot;&gt;Profilo&lt;/a&gt;&#10;            &lt;a href=&quot;#competenze&quot;&gt;Competenze&lt;/a&gt;&#10;            &lt;a href=&quot;#progetti&quot;&gt;Progetti&lt;/a&gt;&#10;            &lt;a href=&quot;#contatti&quot;&gt;Contatti&lt;/a&gt;&#10;&lt;a href=&quot;capolavoro.html&quot;&gt;Capolavoro&lt;/a&gt;&#10;&#10;        &lt;/nav&gt;&#10;        &lt;button id=&quot;themeBtn&quot; class=&quot;theme-toggle&quot; type=&quot;button&quot; aria-label=&quot;Cambia tema&quot;&gt;Tema chiaro&lt;/button&gt;&#10;    &lt;/div&gt;&#10;&lt;/header&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;main class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;&#10;&#10;    &lt;section class=&quot;hero reveal&quot; id=&quot;hero&quot;&gt;&#10;        &lt;div&gt;&#10;            &lt;h1&gt;Ciao, sono Riccardo: studente di quinta al Liceo Scientifico di Bitetto (BA)&lt;/h1&gt;&#10;            &lt;p class=&quot;subtitle&quot;&gt;&#10;                Sono una persona curiosa che crede nel valore del lavoro ben fatto e della sincerità. Non mi piacciono i giri di parole: preferisco i fatti.            &lt;/p&gt;&#10;            &lt;div class=&quot;pill-row&quot; aria-label=&quot;Parole chiave profilo&quot;&gt;&#10;                &lt;span class=&quot;pill&quot;&gt;Problem solving&lt;/span&gt;&#10;                &lt;span class=&quot;pill&quot;&gt;Lavoro di squadra&lt;/span&gt;&#10;                &lt;span class=&quot;pill&quot;&gt;Perfezionista&lt;/span&gt;&#10;                &lt;span class=&quot;pill&quot;&gt;Capacità decisionale&lt;/span&gt;&#10;            &lt;/div&gt;&#10;        &lt;/div&gt;&#10;&#10;        &lt;aside class=&quot;hero-card&quot; aria-label=&quot;Scheda rapida&quot;&gt;&#10;            &lt;img class=&quot;avatar&quot; src=&quot;immagini/fotoprofilo2.JPEG&quot; alt=&quot;Foto profilo di Riccardo Priore&quot; /&gt;&#10;            &lt;p class=&quot;meta&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bitetto (BA)&lt;/strong&gt; | 19 anni&lt;/p&gt;&#10;            &lt;p&gt;&#10;                Obiettivo: iscrivermi a Ingegneria Edile e lavorare in autonomia sia nella realizzazione di nuove costruzioni sia negli interventi di restauro e rigenerazione dell'esistente.&#10;            &lt;/p&gt;&#10;        &lt;/aside&gt;&#10;    &lt;/section&gt;&#10;&#10;    &lt;section id=&quot;profilo&quot; class=&quot;reveal&quot;&gt;&#10;        &lt;h2&gt;Profilo personale&lt;/h2&gt;&#10;        &lt;div class=&quot;grid-2&quot;&gt;&#10;            &lt;article class=&quot;card&quot;&gt;&#10;                &lt;h3&gt;Formazione&lt;/h3&gt;&#10;                &lt;p class=&quot;meta&quot;&gt;Liceo Scientifico - Bitetto (BA) | 2021 - 2026&lt;/p&gt;&#10;                &lt;p&gt;&#10;                    Media scolastica più che discreta in particolare nelle materie umanistiche, e con interesse crescente per le materie scientifiche in particolare l'Informatica.&#10;                &lt;/p&gt;&#10;                            &lt;/article&gt;&#10;&#10;            &lt;article class=&quot;card&quot;&gt;&#10;                &lt;h3&gt;Esperienze e attività&lt;/h3&gt;&#10;                &lt;p&gt;&#10;                    In più occasioni ho collaborato con l'istituto scolastico per la documentazione video e la regia digitale di eventi ufficiali. Ho partecipato attivamente a una serie di incontri culturali e formativi in ambito teatrale e non.                 &#10; &lt;/p&gt;&#10;                &lt;div class=&quot;highlights&quot; aria-label=&quot;Attivita extra&quot;&gt;&#10;                    &lt;span class=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;Eventi scolastici&lt;/span&gt;&#10;                    &lt;span class=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;Competenze digitali&lt;/span&gt;&#10;                    &lt;span class=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;Eventi teatrali&lt;/span&gt;&#10;                &lt;/div&gt;&#10;            &lt;/article&gt;&#10;        &lt;/div&gt;&#10;    &lt;/section&gt;&#10;&#10;    &lt;section id=&quot;competenze&quot; class=&quot;reveal&quot;&gt;&#10;        &lt;h2&gt;Competenze&lt;/h2&gt;&#10;        &lt;div class=&quot;card&quot;&gt;&#10;            &lt;div class=&quot;skills&quot;&gt;&#10;                &lt;div class=&quot;skill&quot;&gt;&#10;                    &lt;div class=&quot;skill-label&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Matematica&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;70%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#10;                    &lt;div class=&quot;bar&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-level=&quot;70&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#10;                &lt;/div&gt;&#10;                &lt;div class=&quot;skill&quot;&gt;&#10;                    &lt;div class=&quot;skill-label&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Italiano&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;70%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#10;                    &lt;div class=&quot;bar&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-level=&quot;70&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#10;                &lt;/div&gt;&#10;                &lt;div class=&quot;skill&quot;&gt;&#10;                    &lt;div class=&quot;skill-label&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Storia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;80%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#10;                    &lt;div class=&quot;bar&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-level=&quot;80&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#10;                &lt;/div&gt;&#10;                &lt;div class=&quot;skill&quot;&gt;&#10;                    &lt;div class=&quot;skill-label&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Scienze naturali&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;70%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#10;                    &lt;div class=&quot;bar&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-level=&quot;70&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#10;                &lt;/div&gt;&#10;            &lt;/div&gt;&#10;        &lt;/div&gt;&#10;    &lt;/section&gt;&#10;&#10;    &lt;section id=&quot;progetti&quot; class=&quot;reveal&quot;&gt;&#10;        &lt;h2&gt;Progetti PCTO&lt;/h2&gt;&#10;        &lt;article class=&quot;card project-list&quot;&gt;&#10;            &lt;div class=&quot;project&quot;&gt;&#10;                &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;project-title-link&quot; href=&quot;lavoroAzienda.html&quot; aria-label=&quot;Apri progetto Lavoro in Azienda&quot;&gt;Lavoro in Azienda&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&#10;                Una piccola descrizione del lavoro in azienda.&#10;            &lt;/div&gt;&#10;            &lt;div class=&quot;project&quot;&gt;&#10;                &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;project-title-link&quot; href=&quot;gitaInGrecia.html&quot; aria-label=&quot;Apri progetto Gita in Grecia&quot;&gt;Gita in Grecia&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&#10;                Piccola descrizione dell'esperienza in Grecia&#10;            &lt;/div&gt;&#10;            &lt;div class=&quot;project&quot;&gt;&#10;                &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;project-title-link&quot; href=&quot;LiceoMatematico.html&quot; aria-label=&quot;Apri progetto Corso Liceo Matematico&quot;&gt;Corso Liceo Matematico Ed. 4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&#10;                Piccola descrizione anche di questo&#10;            &lt;/div&gt;&#10;        &lt;/article&gt;&#10;    &lt;/section&gt;&#10;&#10;    &lt;section id=